

 TITLE:    Ozzfest - 10th Anniversary
 DATE:     06-10-2008
 QUALITY:  DVD
 GENRE:    Metal
 ARCHIVES: 74x100
 VIDEO:    Untouched
 AUDIO:    English 2.0
 STRIPPEd: Nothing
 SUBS:     Hungarian
 SOURCE:   Retail PAL DVD
 NOTES:    The longest running rock tour in history comes home at last – on DVD – celebrating
           10 years on the road! Go inside the Ozzfest Tour’s 10th year, with 60,000 fans at
           the UK show to the 103o heat of the back lots in Camden, NJ. Ozzy, Sharon & Jack
           turn out to show, and tell, how a simple idea became one of rock’s biggest festivals.
           The artists and fans of Ozzfest became a mush of togetherness and the music, well,
           that’s what it’s all about! Ozzy and his festival are now multi-generational and 
           fans, young and old, show up to prove it.
